pan style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聲inginging~~</span></span><br />\n1:41各種<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">癡~~</span></span>情<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">癡&uarr;心&uarr;&uarr;癡&uarr;&uarr;</span></span>纏<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">癡&uarr;&uarr;哀</span></span>亦都經過<br />\n2:02還是惹我<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">心&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;</span></span>一傾再傾<br />\n2:06獻出<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;</span></span>誠<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;知&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;真&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;</span></span>人<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;</span></span>  相落實<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">了↗↗</span></span>角<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">色~~~~~~~~~~~~~&rdquo;ki&rdquo; </span></span> (2:17)<br />\n4:19 每次激情舞<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">步↗~</span></span>抒情<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">歌&uarr;曲&uarr;</span></span>有你掌聲<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">伴~~~~&rdquo;oon&rdquo; </span></span> 還是惹我<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">心&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;~~</span></span>一<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">傾&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;~~</span></span>再<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">傾&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;~~~</span></span><br />\n4:36 獻出<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;</span></span>誠<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;知&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;真&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;</span></span>人<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;↕↕~</span></span>  相落<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&rdquo;實&rdquo;了↗↗</span></span>角<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">色~~~~~~~~~~~~~</span></span><br />\n<br />\n5:22 開始<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兩大阿姐互笠高帽環節: </span></span><br />\nDO 姐: 呢首歌呢相當之好聽<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">喎~~~~!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n阿姐: 我都有少少感動呀 (DO: 係呀!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n真係唔經唔覺喺呢行都50年, 你都40年<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">啦呵~~</span> (好重火藥味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\nDO 姐: 唔好講我嗰筆 !!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (汪:哦呵<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&rdquo;呵~~&rdquo;</span></span>呵呵<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呵</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n汪氏偉論時刻:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">藝員只要有觀眾嘅掌聲呢, 係會繼續呢係演出嘅!!! </span></span><br />\n台下慘叫聲: 呀!!!!!!!!!!!!! [/red][/size=6]<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span s